explanations.description: Adjectives, in particular those with suffixes "-ic", "-ive", "-al", "-ly", "-ous" and "-ful" that are used to describe or modify nouns, often with strong connotations, such as "explosive", "homophobic", "revolutionary", "artistic", "good", "bad", "smart", "offensive", "stressful", "educational" and "terrorist".
